=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一年後</span></span></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我經已係</span></span>"},{"pid":"3836fefe58ec8e6d397f1451b1f137c7c8b02ab5","tid":22140,"uid":50610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T09:45:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">校長條八婆</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阿木</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你唔好再叫阿木啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你索性就叫條廢柴吧啦</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一年後</span></span></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我經已係</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">廢柴</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"df8064da3cee580a029d1dda5cccb0e12013bd5e","tid":22140,"uid":6166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T09:48:29.000Z","msg":"「高橋涼介，你幾時同我走翻轉呀？」<br />\n「如果你跑贏曬群馬山路所有嘅車手，就同你走翻轉囉。」<br />\n「山路？」<br />\n「係落山，全日本嘅落山路。<br />\n咁由聽日起，你喺南面開始，我由北面開始，同唔同山路嘅車手鬥，睇下邊個贏得多，好冇呀？」<br />\n「你唔係諗住落場架咩？」<br />\n「落場？都係山路好玩啲⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n「我返黎喇。嗯？<br />\n想點呀？」<br />\n「喂！老婆！幫我⋯⋯換左條底褲！」<br />\n<br />\n「衰仔！做乜偷左我條底褲呀？<br />\n去邊呀？」<br />\n「我返學呀」<br />\n「返學？放暑假返咩學呀？成日都唔見左人，都唔知係咪去做鴨！<br />\n嗯⋯⋯咦？女裝黎嘅？」<br />\n<br />\n「知唔知咩係神呀？<br />\n神以前都係人，不過佢做到人做唔到嘅野，之後佢就係神喇。<br />\n一年前！校長條八婆踢左我出校！<br />\n佢同我講，佢話：「呀木，你不如唔好叫呀木，你索性就叫條廢柴啦你。」<br />\n之後我諗得好清楚<br />\n我要話比全世界人知道！<br />\n我呀木，唔係廢柴。<br />\n我！要！做！車！手！<br />\n一年喇。我已經係秋名山車神，士必 STAR 車隊嘅老闆。」<br />\n「嗯？你唔係舊年至考到牌咩？」<br />\n「拿，呢啲咪就係叫做資質囉。好簡單架啫，姐飄移咁，點飄呀？<br />\n一入灣，拉拉手掣，架車 bell 一 bell 咁囉。咁又點呀？型囉。」<br />\n「架車⋯⋯架車咪好慢囉？」<br />\n「咁應該點飄呢？」<br />\n「咁你咪踏盡油門，過灣嘅時候唔好太慢，嗯⋯⋯然後反駄，之後⋯⋯」<br />\n「你咁樣反架車咪跌左落山咁你咪死囉。唉不過算啦，我唔怪你，你同我一齊考到牌，到今日連軚盤都未掂過。<br />\n不如咁啦！加入我車隊！」<br />\n「嗯？冇車呀！」<br />\n「唔洗車嘅！你黎幫我洗車架姐！你諗下，我揸車，你洗車，幾有前途呀！<br />\n尼，兄弟，飲杯！奶好呀，有咩好呀？又高鈣，又有蛋白質。最緊要係咩啊？明目丫嘛！<br />\n車手最緊要係咩啊？對眼。」<br />\n<br />\n「喂去睇戲咯？好啊！」<br />\n「唔去得呀要翻 parttime 呀⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n「喂！睇夠未呀？」<br />\n「二B高班，茂木夏樹，今日白色。」<br />\n「嗯？好好玩呀？」<br />\n「好緊張咁喎，好熟架？」<br />\n「唔係呀。」<br />\n「唔係？聽講你上個禮拜為左佢，同隔離班呀狼狗嘈左獲金架喎！」<br />\n「返工喇！」<br />\n「咦係喎，我都夠鐘去㩒錢添。」<br />\n「好〜開工！」"},{"pid":"b544b89cfd1ed61978a6d28a712f7ed356cdaf1f","tid":22140,"uid":34971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T09:48:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">校長條八婆</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阿木</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你唔好再叫阿木啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\