Time":"2016-12-04T16:40:05.000Z","msg":"你無得同我架Fc鬥啊&hellip;鬥鬥鬥鬥&hellip;Fc鬥啊"},{"pid":"3157dcba07a51ae8af76067b1d319bea50345fba","tid":22140,"uid":42281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T02:58:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">咁架車咪好慢囉</span>"}]}